watch that come back

00:17:05.989 --> 00:17:08.030
and turn into this beautiful,
pale, creamy sauce.

00:17:08.030 --> 00:17:09.560
So I'm going to
start and then I'll

00:17:09.560 --> 00:17:11.268
stop to show you guys
what it looks like.

00:17:20.231 --> 00:17:20.730
All right.

