00:18:59.610 --> 00:19:02.470
So it can sit in the
fridge for a couple days.

00:19:02.470 --> 00:19:05.150
People even freeze it,
which we don't recommend,

00:19:05.150 --> 00:19:06.340
but it does work.

00:19:06.340 --> 00:19:08.620
You just have to put it
back into the Robot Coupe

00:19:08.620 --> 00:19:10.090
