AUDIENCE: More.

00:29:28.157 --> 00:29:28.990
SPEAKER: More, more.

00:29:28.990 --> 00:29:31.172
MICHAEL SOLOMONOV: OK.

00:29:31.172 --> 00:29:32.622
SPEAKER: There you go.

